  <name>Chorus</name>
  <summary>View the lyrics for your currently playing music</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Chorus watches whatever music player is running on your system and shows
      synced or plain lyrics for the current track.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Follows any music player automatically, or lets you pick one manually</li>
      <li>Synced lyrics scroll and highlight the current line as the song plays</li>
      <li>Blurred cover art as a live background</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
